The worn Isa entity
  Container Taking clothing.
End The worn.

Every clothing Isa object
  Has size 1.
  Verb wear
    Check Sum Of size Directly In worn > 1
      Else "You can't wear anything more."
    Does
      Locate this In worn.
  End Verb.
End Every clothing.

The robe Isa clothing In worn
End The robe.

The shirt Isa clothing At l
End The shirt.

The l Isa location
End The l.

Start At l.